comments: LLB and LLS show Richardson (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position on Booker (PHX) and makes incidental contact to his arm after the release of his pass.
LLB shows Ayton (PHX) has his arm extended and delivers contact to Wade (MIA) that affects his shot attempt.
Wade (MIA) makes contact with his teammate Adebayo (MIA) during the rebound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Oubre Jr. (PHX) has a foot inside the three-point arc before the release of the free throw.
RLS shows Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes a natural basketball move and he inadvertently contact with Olynyk's (MIA) shoulder.
[Observable in enhanced video] Booker (PHX) takes more than two steps after gathering the ball.
Richardson (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Oubre Jr. (PHX).
Adebayo (MIA) is late to establish himself in the path of Johnson (PHX) during the dribble hand-off and he extends his hip out to deliver contact.
RLS shows Waiters (MIA) makes contact to the face of Booker (PHX) when he swipes at the ball on the driving shot attempt and the contact affects his ability to finish at the basket.
Ayton (PHX) jumps toward Waiters (MIA) but avoids initiating any contact that affects his jump shot attempt.  The contact is initiated by Waiters in an attempt to draw the foul.
Johnson (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Adebayo (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ayton (PHX) firms up in a screening position in the path of Richardson (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LLS shows Wade (MIA) makes incidental  contact to the lower body of Ayton (PHX) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Ayton (PHX) is in the lane for less than three seconds when his shot is imminent.
LLB and PXP show Johnson (PHX) engages on the pick and puts an arm across the chest of Adebayo (MIA) but the contact is incidental.
Richardson (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Booker (PHX) that affects his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) dislodges Bridges (PHX) and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
LLB and LAR show Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes contact to the arm of Adebayo (MIA) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Oubre Jr. (PHX).
